A R E S O L U T I O N
Honoring Stewart’s Root Beer Drive-in on its
Centennial.
WHEREAS, The members of the House of Representatives of the 136th 1
General Assembly of Ohio are pleased to extend special recognition to 2
Stewart’s Root Beer Drive-in on the memorable occasion of its 3
One Hundredth Anniversary; and 4
WHEREAS, Recognition of this prestigious milestone is, indeed, a 5
fitting tribute to Stewart’s Root Beer Drive-in, for over the past one 6
hundred years, this fine business has achieved a praiseworthy record 7
of service. For a century, this seasonal eatery has gained the 8
appreciation of countless patrons with its unique menu of ice-cold 9
root beer floats, cheeseburgers, coney dogs, milkshakes, and more, all 10
delivered by car hops, and it has continually demonstrated its 11
exemplary commitment to the highest standards of quality; and 12
WHEREAS, The success of Stewart’s Root Beer Drive-in is a 13
justifiable source of pride and an outstanding reflection not only on 14
the business itself but also on its astute management and hard-working 15
employees. Due to their vision and initiative, this respected 16
institution has earned the gratitude and appreciation of many 17
satisfied customers, and they are truly deserving of high praise; and 18
WHEREAS, Over the past one hundred years, Stewart’s Root Beer 19
Drive-in has enhanced the quality of life within Marion and the 20
surrounding area, and it has distinguished itself as a true icon of 21
the community. We are certain that as this worthy enterprise maintains 22
its dedication to service and achievement, it will continue to 23
prosper, and will uphold the tradition of excellence that has long 24
been its hallmark; therefore be it 25

